timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 11’ - Paparatto with a perfect tackle just inside his own 18 box to knock ball away from attack. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 11' Crucial slide from Paparatto to intercept Dovale's through ball on the edge of the box. Dwyer was nearly through on goal. 0-0 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 13' Good movement from SKC in the attacking third. Dovale has a left-footed shot from the top of the box and Peay blocks it. 0-0 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 14' Saad has a free kick from the left side 40 yards out, and he swings it over everyone's head. Goal kick. 0-0 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 14’ - SKC with a long FK from distance that sails long out for a goal kick. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 16’ - Fernández steals ball from Nagamura near midfield but heavy touch goes too far. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 16' Strong run toward goal from Zizzo, and he draws a foul outside the right edge of the box. Set piece coming. 0-0 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 17' Dwyer strikes a low, left-footed curler around the wall, but Weber gets down low to push it wide of goal. A good attempt there. #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 17’ - SAVE! Dwyer curls FK from just outside the box and Weber with a nice diving save to his right. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 19' Gorgeous lob pass over the top from Dovale to Nagamura, but Paulo gets whistled for a foul after colliding with Weber. 0-0 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 19’- SKC with ball over the top, Weber off his line to challenge. Ref blows for offside. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: Match ends, Sporting Kansas City 1, Portland Timbers 3.

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: Vote for your #CenturyLinkManoftheMatch from tonight's #USOC2014 win over @SportingKC. VOTE: http://t.co/rTUOeeQN2n. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: Images from the big win in Kansas City. NIGHT IN PICTURES: http://t.co/mIPl4aVRIq #RCTID #USOC2014 http://t.co/djPta5QUIA

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: Images from the big win in Kansas City. NIGHT IN PICTURES: http://t.co/mIPl4aVRIq #RCTID #USOC2014 http://t.co/djPta5QUIA

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: So...@SoundersFC. We meet again. Let’s do this. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.text: Fernández with brace as Timbers beat SKC in fifth round of #USOC2014. RECAP: http://t.co/55Ca9VdfgX #RCTID http://t.co/opnaCklJTK

timelineItems.text: Fernández with brace as Timbers beat SKC in fifth round of #USOC2014. RECAP: http://t.co/55Ca9VdfgX #RCTID http://t.co/opnaCklJTK

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: .@AWEBS13: "We all believe in each other and it’s good." QUOTES & NOTES: http://t.co/62awpSLrtY #RCTID #USOC2014 http://t.co/22XtrUcs5d

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: .@AWEBS13: "We all believe in each other and it’s good." QUOTES & NOTES: http://t.co/62awpSLrtY #RCTID #USOC2014 http://t.co/22XtrUcs5d

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 22’ - Nice buildup from Portland. Alhassan down right wing, ball played across the middle but SKC clears away. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 21' Saad and Nagamura combine well down the left, and Paulo's low cross from the left side of the box is thumped clear by O'Rourke. #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 23' Saad fires just wide! Looked a lot like the goal he scored last week, but his low strike from outside the box misses narrowly. #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 25' Dwyer receives a pass in a central position 35 yards from goal and is taken down by Paparatto. Foul called, set piece for SKC. #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 26’ - SKC with tricky short FK to Dwyer. His cross back into six is alertly cleared away by Paparatto. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 27' Alhassan carries the ball 40+ yards and is taken down just outside the box. The resulting free kick is blocked by the SKC wall. #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 28’ - Johnson’s FK drilled into wall. KC clears but POR play ball back in. Urruti’s shot forces a save. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 29' Urruti's low shot from the right side of the box sizzles just wide of the far post! Still 0-0 #SKCvPOR #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 29’ - Great work in the midfield. Zakuani w/ball through to Urruti. His tight angle shot jusssst wide. Timbers attacking. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 29’ - Timbers sub in McKenzie for Paparatto. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 30' Portland takes the lead as Gaston Fernandez slides a left-footed shot past Gruenebaum from 12 yards out. 0-1 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 30’ - GOALLLLL!!!!! Fernández makes it 1-0 with a clutch strike from inside the area!!! #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: Lineups are announced and players are warming up.

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: Alhassan beat Sinovic on the right edge of the box and his cross was deflected into Fernandez's path. He made no mistake. 0-1 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: Great cutback pass from Alhassan there to set up Fernández’s goal. That is #LaGata’s third goal in the #USOC2014. #RCTID

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 33’ - Urruti plays great ball ahead to Alhassan who was wide open. Ball skips a bit and skitters away. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 33' Urruti plays a perfect diagonal ball to Alhassan who was through on goal, but he couldn't control the pass. Chance is gone. #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 36’ - SKC pushing into Timbers’ 18. Defense holds, can’t quite clear. Weber finally covers low skipping shot. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 38' Ellis curls a cross to the far post, Saad does fantastically to sneak past two defenders, then Dovale's shot is blocked! 0-1 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 41' Alhassan streaks down the right but Palmer-Brown does well to recover and makes an important challenge on the edge of the box. #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 41’ - Johnson with great diagonal ball to Alhassan on the sprint. Ball is tackled away by SKC on edge of the area. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 44' SKC possessing patiently in the final moments of the half. Can they grab an equalizer before the break? 0-1 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 45' Excellent lob pass over the top from Dovale to Sinovic, but the full back is narrowly offside. Good vision by the Spaniard. 0-0 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: HALFTIME. @SportingKC trails @TimbersFC 1-0 after a 30th-minute goal from Gaston Fernandez. #SKCvPOR #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Sporting Kansas City
timelineItems.text: HALFTIME: The Fernandez goal stands as @TimbersFC take a 1-0 lead into the break #SKCvPOR #USOC2014 https://t.co/nXVJht3HSY

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: Halftime. Timbers lead Sporting Kansas City 1-0 via #LaGata Fernández goal. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: First Half ends, Sporting Kansas City 0, Portland Timbers 1.

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 0-1 #SKCvPOR. HT stats: Goals: Fernandez 30' Shots (OG): SKC 6 (3), POR 3 (2) Fouls: SKC 7-10 POR Corners: SKC 3-0 POR Offside: SKC 2-1 POR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: And we're back underway @SportingPark. The home side will attack the @KCCauldron end here in the second half. 0-1 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.comment: Second Half begins Sporting Kansas City 0, Portland Timbers 1.

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: Second half is underway for the Timbers and Sporting. Portland leads 1-0. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 48' Dovale floats another pass over the top but Saad can't quite track it down as Weber comes out to collect. 0-1 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 4’ - Alhassan tries to play long cross to Zakuani on the opposite side but ball carries a little and out for goal kick. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 6' Paparatto whistle for a foul after taking down Dwyer on the right wing. SKC wins a corner kick shortly thereafter. 0-0 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 50' Good one-two between Zizzo and Olum, but Zizzo's cross to the far post is a little heavy. SKC retains possession... 0-1 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 51' SKC with a giveaway at midfield but the end result is a tame shot from Fernandez and a routine save from Gruenebaum. 0-1 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 51’ - Zakuani cuts in from the right hand side and fires a low shot on goal. Gruenebaum with the save. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 53' Dwyer chips a cross into the six-yard area but no one made a run into the middle, and now Portland has possession. 0-1 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 52’ - SKC’s Dwyer goes 1v1 with O’Rourke. Defender stands tall and Dwyer’s shot goes wide for goal kick. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Sporting Kansas City
timelineItems.text: #SportingKC's @b_feilhaber22 joining @CalWilliamsSKC and @JakeYadrich on the #SKCvPOR broadcast. Tune in --> http://t.co/DzTxSZEtb0

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 55' Zakuani is flagged offside after receiving a pass on the right side of the penalty area. 0-1 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 56' Zakuani makes a weaving run into the box and is taken down. Penalty kick given to the Timbers... 0-1 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 56’ - PENALTY! Zakuani in on goal and Collin takes him down. Ref points to the spot! #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: Penalty Portland Timbers. Steve Zakuani draws a foul in the penalty area.
Penalty conceded by Aurélien Collin (Sporting Kansas City) after a foul in the penalty area.

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 57' Will Johnson buries the penalty low past Gruenebaum. Timbers lead 2-0. #SKCvPOR #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 57’ - GOALLLL!!! @WillJohnson04 hits PK with authority and Timbers lead 2-0!!!! #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 59' Yellow card given to Aurelien Collin for dissent. 0-2 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 6' Incredible save from Andrew Weber to deny Sal Zizzo's header off a corner kick! 0-0 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 6’ - KC whip in a corner that Zizzo gets on frame but Weber tips over the bar! #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 59’ - Collin receives a yellow for SKC. KC also brings in Peterson for Zizzo. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 60' SUB for SKC: Jacob Peterson replaces Sal Zizzo as Sporting KC looks to erase a 2-0 deficit. #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 61' Dovale again pulling the strings in attack as he lobs a pass for Saad, whose cross is blocked out for a corner kick. 0-2 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 62’ - Dangerous ball in by SKC for Saad. McKenzie swoops in to knock ball away at top of six. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 64’ - Dwyer with time in front of the net. He shoots. Blocked. Ellis shoots. Blocked. Corner for SKC. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 65’ - Timbers bring in Michael Harrington for Steve Zakuani. Timbers lead SKC 2-0. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 64' Dwyer and Ellis both have their shots blocked from close range inside the box. Home side increasing the pressure now... 0-2 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 65' Havoc in the box as the ball pings around in the air, and Portland eventually manages to clear. 0-2 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 67’ - Harrington, Fernández and Alhassan work ball around area on counter. Alhassan’s shot is wide. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 68’ - GOALLLLL!!! #LAGATA AGAIN! Urruti with blast on frame. Rebound falls to Fernández who easily pounces! 3-0! #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 68' Portland grabs another goal. Urruti had his shot blocked by Gruenebaum, but Fernandez was there to tap in the rebound. 0-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: Zizzo dove for a header at the near post, and Weber tapped it inches over the crossbar. It was heading into the net... 0-0 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 71' SUB for SKC: C.J. Sapong replaces Dom Dwyer. 0-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: #LaGata. Two #USOC2014 games. Two braces. So hot right now. #RCTID http://t.co/4QJtkhxRNd

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: #LaGata. Two #USOC2014 games. Two braces. So hot right now. #RCTID http://t.co/4QJtkhxRNd

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 71’ - SKC brings in Sapong for Dwyer. Portland leading 3-0. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: Penalty conceded by Danny O'Rourke (Portland Timbers) with a hand ball in the penalty area.

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 72' Penalty kick given to Sporting KC! Dovale lobbed another great pass to Saad, whose cross/shot was hand-balled by O'Rourke. 0-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 72’ - PENALTY for SKC. Saad cuts ball back in area and it hits O’Rourke’s arm. Ref points to spot. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 73’ - GOAL. SKC’s Saad converts penalty in lower left corner. Timbers still lead 3-1. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 73' Saad dispatches the penalty, and @SportingKC have pulled one back! 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 73' Saad gives SKC a lifeline with his fourth career Open Cup goal. He's one shy of tying the club record in the tournament. 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 75' Good chance for Sapong as he collects a pass from Palmer-Brown, but his low strike is saved by Weber. 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 75’ - SKC trying to build on goal. Sapong fires a shot but Weber calmly makes save. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 76' Sporting KC with their tails up after Saad's PK. Two more goals isn't out of the question. 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 77' Sapong gets on the end of the corner kick, but his goal-bound shot is blocked! 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: Correction: Alhassan guarded that near post like a boss. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 78' Saad cuts into the middle from the left and curls a fine effort on goal, but Weber saves. 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 77’ - CLEARED OFF THE LINE! Harrington manages to knock ball away off dangerous SKC corner. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 80' Yellow card shown to Kevin Ellis after taking Urruti down from behind near midfield. 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 8' Alhassan tries a through ball for Maxi Urruti down the right flank but Collin intercepts and SKC has possession. 0-0 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 80’ - Fernandez goes down hard near midfield but stays in. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 81' Peterson does well to get down the right side and fire a low cross into the box. Blocked out for a corner. 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 81’ - Another SKC corner but Weber confidently leaps to grab ball out of the air. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 82' SUB for POR: Fanendo Adi replaces Gaston Fernandez, who was two goals on the night. 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 82’ - Timbers bring in Adi for Fernández. Great game for #LaGata as his brace has Timbers leading SKC 3-1. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 84' SUB for SKC: Alex Martinez replaces Paulo Nagamura. That's SKC's final substitution of the match. 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 85’ - Alhassan receives a yellow card ahead of a Timbers free kick. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 86' Great work from the newly introduced Martinez to create space and chip a ball into the six-yard area, but McKenzie heads clear. #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 86’ - Harrington battles SKC’s Martinez on the right side. Martinez’s chip into box headed away by McKenzie. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 88' SKC wins a free kick 25 yards from goal, and Saad's curling effort sails well over the bar. 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 88’ - SKC lines up FK from 30 yards out and Saad skies it into the stands. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 89' Peterson threads a wonderful through ball to Dovale inside the box, but the Spaniard's cross is blocked and the chance is gone. #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 9' Stoppage in play as Nagamura goes down near the center circle. Looks like he'll be alright. 0-0 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 89’ - O’Rourke with great tackle of Sapong at top of six to eliminate SKC chance. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: There will be four minutes of added time. Timbers leading 3-1. #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 90+2' Collin ventures forward and he's flagged offside in the box. 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: 92’ - Collin offside but Weber made elegant save on his shot. #AllSafe #RCTID #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 90+4' Free kick for SKC on the edge of the box, and Dovale's curling effort hits the crossbar... 1-3 #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: FULL TIME. @TimbersFC 3, @SportingKC 1. A Gaston Fernandez brace leads Portland to the Open Cup quarterfinals. #SKCvPOR

timelineItems.name: Portland Timbers
timelineItems.text: Full time! Timbers defeat Sporting Kansas City 3-1 in the #USOC2014 fifth round!!!! Brace for #LaGata and PK from @WillJohnson04. #RCTID

timelineItems.comment: Second Half ends, Sporting Kansas City 1, Portland Timbers 3.
